snippet: Incollect.com, thehighboy.com and thefinest.com are among the new websites that help antiques collectors click and buy.
abstract: Eve M Kahn Antiques column; incollect.com, thehighboy.com and thefinest.com are among new websites that help antiques collectors click and buy; exhibition of antiques produced in the South opens at DeWitt Wallace Decorative Arts Museum; artworks and antiques collected by Art Nouveau scholar and dealer Victor Arwas will be displayed at Sainsbury Center for Visual Arts at University of East Anglia in England.
lead_paragraph: Incollect.com, thehighboy.com and thefinest.com are among the new websites that help antiques collectors click and buy.

headline.main: New Antiques Websites Join Crowded Field
headline.print_headline: Going, Going, Click: Online Bidding Grows
